NK037(ji)014:0: mgon po beng gi sgrub thabs dbang chog dang dbang bcas pa bzhugs /
NK037(ji)014:2: bstan srung dpa' bo legs ldan che //
NK037(ji)014:3: bing 'dzin mgon po la btud nas //
NK037(ji)014:4: de yi sgrub thabs khyad par rnams //
NK037(ji)014:5: gsal byed snying por dril te bshad //
NK037(ji)014:6: 'dir mgon po beng gi sgrub thabs dang 'brel bar dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK037(ji)014:7: sbyor ba yo byad kyi shoms /
NK037(ji)014:8: dngos gzhi sgrub pa'i thabs dang /
NK037(ji)014:10: dang po yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK037(ji)014:11: gnas dus 'dzom pa la rten gyi mdun du /
NK037(ji)014:12: chos 'byung mthing nag phyi rol du thod ra me ri dang bcas pas bskor ba bri /
NK037(ji)014:13: de yi dbus su rten gtor dang mthar mchod gtor sogs kyis tshang bar bskor ro //
NK037(ji)014:15: bdag bskyed dang mchod rdzas byin rlabs sngon du 'gro bas /
NK037(ji)014:17: stong pa'i ngang las srung ba'i 'khor lo yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK037(ji)014:18: 'jigs rung dur khrod chen pos bskor ba'i thod mkhar
NK037(ji)014:19: brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus su pad nyi
NK037(ji)014:20: dang bam chen bsnol ba'i steng du k+sha yig 'od
NK037(ji)014:21: kyi 'phro 'du las legs ldan nag po sred med
NK037(ji)014:22: kyi bu / sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK037(ji)014:23: g.yas tsan+dana gyi beng chen nor bus mtshan pa beng
NK037(ji)014:24: stod nas me 'bar zhing beng smad nas chu 'brub
NK037(ji)014:25: pa / beng gi nang nas lha min gyi dmag tshogs spro ba /
NK037(ji)014:26: g.yon lcags par nad sna tshogs kyis gang ba dkur brten pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin pa /
NK037(ji)014:27: za 'og gi ber chen gsol zhing gser gyi ska rags bcings pa /
NK037(ji)014:28: zhabs la sag lhwam gsol ba /
NK037(ji)014:29: thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang /
NK037(ji)014:30: thod rlon lnga bcu'i do shal can /
NK037(ji)014:32: spyan gsum sdang mig tu gzigs pa /
NK037(ji)014:33: mche ba gtsigs shing ljags 'dril ba /
NK037(ji)014:34: sma ra dang smin ma dbu skra kham nag 'bar zhing /
NK037(ji)014:35: g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK037(ji)014:36: g.yon du b+ho las re ma t+ai smug nag ma
NK037(ji)014:37: mo'i chas can khram shing dang nad rkyal 'dzin pa
NK037(ji)014:38: / drel rta rkang gsum la chibs pa /
NK037(ji)014:39: mtha' bskor du nag po stong lha ma srin sde brgyad /
NK037(ji)014:40: ma mo chen mo bdun 'khor dang bcas pas yongs su bskor ba'o //
NK037(ji)014:41: ye shes pa spyan 'dren nas mchod bstod kyi mthar
NK037(ji)014:42: thug pa'i bar 'di nyid kyi mchod chog snga ma
NK037(ji)014:43: rnams nas snying po btus pa ci rigs bya ba
NK037(ji)014:44: yin mod kyi / don gyi gtso bo la khyad
NK037(ji)014:45: par med cing cho ga'i ngo bo thams cad gcig
NK037(ji)014:46: yin pas stag zhon gyi skabs su bshad pa ltar
NK037(ji)014:47: 'don pa spos pas chog pa yin no //
NK037(ji)014:48: bstod pa rnam grangs shin tu mang yang /
NK037(ji)014:51: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK037(ji)014:52: yang dag gsang ba'i sku gcig byung ba ni //
NK037(ji)014:53: mgon po beng ma gsang ba'i skur bstan pa //
NK037(ji)014:54: mi 'gyur khro bo khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK037(ji)014:55: lha mo gshin rje'i lcam gcig bdud kyi yum //
NK037(ji)014:56: lha srin sde brgyad gnod sbyin ma mo dang //
NK037(ji)014:57: sde dpon nag po stong gi tshogs bcas la //
NK037(ji)014:58: gus pa'i yid kyis phyag 'tshal bstod par bgyi //
NK037(ji)014:61: ma h+aa k+aa la rak+sha du beng ni dzah zhes pa'o //
NK037(ji)014:63: badz+ra yak+sha de wa ma h+aa k+aa la kha kro d+ha h'u /
NK037(ji)014:64: sa ma ya dzahdzah thun ka la rak+sha ni dza rbad /
NK037(ji)014:66: gsum pa dbang gi cho ga ni /
NK037(ji)014:67: 'byung khungs dang cho ga'i khog gcig pa'i phyir stag
NK037(ji)014:68: zhon gyi skabs nyid 'don pa spo ba yin mod
NK037(ji)014:69: / ngo bo gcig pa nyid la yang cho ga'i
NK037(ji)014:70: sgros tha dad pa snang bas rnam pa gsal phyir
NK037(ji)014:74: phur bu sogs yo byad khyad par ba rnams bsags /
NK037(ji)014:75: sgrub mchod 'dod don gsol btab yan rdzogs par byas la /
NK037(ji)014:77: mtshams sbyor ci rigs par bshad nas /
NK037(ji)014:78: rje btsun rdo rje 'dzin pa'i gtso //
NK037(ji)014:79: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi //
NK037(ji)014:80: dri ma thams cad sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)014:81: dbang bskur byin rlabs stsal du gsol //
NK037(ji)014:83: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK037(ji)014:85: gtor ma mgon po 'khor bcas su bskyed la ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK037(ji)014:86: gtor dbang spyi dang mthun snga ma ltar /
NK037(ji)014:88: par bya ste sku'i dbang ngo //
NK037(ji)014:89: slob ma mgon por bskyed pa la phreng ba gtad de /
NK037(ji)014:95: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi rten //
NK037(ji)014:96: gang zhig phyar ba tsam gyis ni //
NK037(ji)014:97: dgra bgegs rdul du rlog byed pa //
NK037(ji)014:98: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK037(ji)014:99: ma h+aa k+aa la rak+sha du beng h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK037(ji)014:102: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub rten //
NK037(ji)014:103: gang zhig dran pa tsam gyis ni //
NK037(ji)014:104: nag po dgyes shing ngoms par byed //
NK037(ji)014:105: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK037(ji)014:106: ma h+aa k+aa la tsit+ta pri tam +aahmh'u a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK037(ji)014:109: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las rten //
NK037(ji)014:110: gang zhig bsgril ba tsam gyis ni //
NK037(ji)014:111: gdul dka' ma lus 'jigs par byed //
NK037(ji)014:112: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK037(ji)014:113: ma h+aa k+aa la dgra bo'i snying la k+ai la ya h'u phata a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK037(ji)014:115: rjes khas blangs yon 'bul rnams dang /
NK037(ji)014:116: stob pa sogs rjes chog rnams kyang gong bzhin no //
NK037(ji)014:117: rjes gnang gi cho ga 'di stag zhon la yang
NK037(ji)014:118: sbyar bas chog ste cho ga'i rnam grangs gcig yin
NK037(ji)014:119: pa'i phyir ro // rnam 'gyur gtum drag gnod sbyin mgon //
NK037(ji)014:120: thogs med mthu mnga' gsang chen sngags //
NK037(ji)014:121: rdo rje theg pa'i bka' srung gtso //
NK037(ji)014:122: beng chen sgrub thabs snying po'i phul //
NK037(ji)014:123: mgon po beng ma'i sgrub thabs bka' gter gnyis ldan
NK037(ji)014:124: gyi lugs su bkod pa'i le'u tshan gter chen 'gyur
NK037(ji)014:125: med rdo rje'i gsung sgrub thabs 'dod 'jo'i bum bzang
